Ref:
http://www.server-world.info/en/note?os=CentOS_7&p=openldap&f=1
http://www.server-world.info/en/note?os=CentOS_7&p=openldap&f=3
http://www.server-world.info/en/note?os=CentOS_7&p=openldap&f=4
